'''髓过氧化物酶'''（{{lang-en|Myeloperoxidase}}，简称为'''MPO'''）是一种由人类[[17号染色体|17号染色体]]上''MPO''基因编码的[[过氧化物酶|过氧化物酶]]<ref name="entrez">{{cite web | title = Entrez Gene: Myeloperoxidase | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?db=gene&cmd=retrieve&list_uids=4353 | accessdate = 2017-04-06 | archive-date = 2010-12-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101205081110/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?db=gene | dead-url = no }}</ref>。MPO主要表达于[[中性粒细胞|中性粒细胞]]（[[白细胞|白细胞]]的一种）中，并产生次卤酸，发挥其[[抗菌|抗菌]]活性<ref name="entrez"/><ref name="pmid15689384">{{cite journal | vauthors = Klebanoff SJ | title = Myeloperoxidase: friend and foe | journal = Journal of Leukocyte Biology | volume = 77 | issue = 5 | pages = 598–625 | date = May 2005 | pmid = 15689384 | doi = 10.1189/jlb.1204697 }}</ref>。髓过氧化物酶是中性粒细胞[[嗜天青顆粒|嗜天青顆粒]]中的一种[[溶酶体|溶酶体]]蛋白，在[[脱颗粒|脱颗粒]]的时候释放到[[胞外|胞外]]<ref name="pmid6192815">{{cite journal | vauthors = Kinkade JM, Pember SO, Barnes KC, Shapira R, Spitznagel JK, Martin LE | title = Differential distribution of distinct forms of myeloperoxidase in different azurophilic granule subpopulations from human neutrophils | journal = Biochemical and Biophysical Research Communications | volume = 114 | issue = 1 | pages = 296–303 | date = Jul 1983 | pmid = 6192815 | doi=10.1016/0006-291x(83)91627-3}}</ref>。MPO内含有一个[[血红素|血红素]]组分，使得富含[[中性粒细胞|中性粒细胞]]的分泌物显示出绿色，这些分泌物包括[[膿|膿]]和[[黏液|黏液]]。

